'''康纳·菲尔兹'''（{{lang-en|Connor Fields}}，{{bd|1992年|9月14日||}}）生于得克萨斯州普莱诺，是一名美国男子自行车运动员，主攻小轮车<ref>{{cite web|url=http://archivepyc.nbcolympics.com/athletes/connor-fields/751183|title=Connor Fields|work=NBC Olympics|accessdate=2020-09-26|archiveurl=https://archive.is/R2sts|archivedate=2020-09-23}}</ref>。菲尔兹童年在[[拉斯维加斯|拉斯维加斯]]长大<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/olympics/cycling/story/_/id/17349259/2016-rio-olympics-connor-field-childhood-prediction-comes-true-bmx-gold|title=Connor Field's childhood prediction comes true with BMX gold|publisher=[[ESPN|ESPN]]|date=2016-08-20|accessdate=2020-09-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190406132424/http://www.espn.com/olympics/cycling/story/_/id/17349259/2016-rio-olympics-connor-field-childhood-prediction-comes-true-bmx-gold|archivedate=2019-04-06}}</ref>，他在7岁时开始参加小轮车比赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.teamusa.org/usa-cycling/athletes/Connor-Fields|title=Connor Fields|work=Team USA|accessdate=2020-09-26|archiveurl=https://archive.is/qshQl|archivedate=2020-09-23}}</ref>，同年他首次获得比赛的奖杯<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.usabmx.com/site/postings/1634|title=At Home with Connor Fields|work=USA BMX|date=2018-12-13|accessdate=2020-09-26|archiveurl=https://archive.is/seSNn|archivedate=2020-09-23}}</ref>。菲尔兹曾在[[2016年夏季奥林匹克运动会|2016年里约奥运]]获得男子小轮车金牌，成为历史上首位获得小轮车项目奥运金牌的美国选手<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.grindtv.com/bike/connor-fields-becomes-first-american-bmx-rider-win-olympic-gold/|title=Connor Fields becomes first American BMX rider to win Olympic gold|work=GRINDTV.com|date=2016-08-19|accessdate=2017-03-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170326051725/http://www.grindtv.com/bike/connor-fields-becomes-first-american-bmx-rider-win-olympic-gold/|archivedate=2017-03-26 }}</ref>。

